            containing mobile phone and tablet keyboards for North, Julev, South,
            Pite, Inari and Skolt Sami. The app is available
            for <a
href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=no.uit.giella.keyboards.Sami"
                >Android</a> and <a
href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/samiske-tastatur/id948386025?ls=1&amp;mt=8"
                >iOS (iPhone and iPad)</a>.</p>

